node.text:
Try this workout on your next leg day -
Hack Squat 4x10
Heel Elevated Goblet Squat (do 10 with weight and 10 body weight) superset with Bulgarian split squats 4x10/12 
Pit shark 4x10
Walking Lunges superset with Sissy Squat 4x12/50

node.text: Really thinking about eating a vegan chkn sandwich with some fries but I’m gonna stay on track with my diet😈

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by MELANIE ANABALON 🌱♌️🇦🇷 in Dallas, Texas with @theomegafitness. May be an image of 1 person, standing and indoor.

node.text: Become aware of the thoughts that arise in your mind but don’t become them because they are not your reality. Sometimes we are even hearing others thoughts... 😂🤭 Thoughts and emotions, acknowledge them (..if you want to) & let them pass through just like everything else in life.  We can be whatever we want or choose to be nothing at all at any moment but if we are prisoners to our thoughts & emotions they’ll manifest even more. 😌

node.text: Don’t ever stop working on your mental and physical health because that’s what carries you through this life. Always strive to be a better you☺️

node.text: I didn’t eat the most nutritious diet while I was away on vacation so my belly has been hurting a tad bit.
